    "description": "Join the Dunzo family as a Marketplace Manager in Lucknow. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Dunzo:\nDunzo is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Learning & development budget\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dunzo!",
